{
  "stem": "3002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the, the Poles always underlined-- when my mother used to go to, to parents' meetings, they always underlined that at home, everybody has to speak Polish only in order to--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and to the parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in order to be perfect in the Polish language.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not anymore.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't use the language anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm glad to speak English",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a general feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't have to come-- have any special encounters with anybody because everybody was aware of it, that the Poles were anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You always have to be careful what you say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you always could be insulted, but you couldn't answer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was common knowledge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm talking about, right now, about high school, and when I was home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those things came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when I was in high school, my older brother had a job in a nearby town, small town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, my older brother used to attend the university in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while he was home, he was-- had a job in a small town near Konskie called Przedborz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, boy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's P-R-Z-E-D-B-O-R-Z.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Przedborz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to keep the books for the Jewish committee there in, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in his time off.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that particular summer, in '39, I was going to him to, spend my vacation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I was off from school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that my-- that time, my brother was already married.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his married family was on the Polish-Russian border, in Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "O-S-T-R-O-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he came home, he worked in, in this little town.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
